Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:53.44,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(30,20)}Just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:09.02,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(30,20)}Like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't take much more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When will it finally rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to divine when the rains will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be blessed by rain in two days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring the jugs out! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Her divination came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:47.58,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an7\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H8C4863&\pos(-2,68)\fscx380\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.61,0:03:47.58,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(70,110)}Cloudless Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Water that soaks not into the earth but instead creeps along its surface
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is but an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though you may pursue it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you will never reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying for rain, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the weather seems unwilling to provide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of any watering holes around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to replenish my supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should spend a few days here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The rains will soon come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She smelled of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The heavens will soon bless us with rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Miss Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rest at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hold a banquet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all welcome to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a traveler passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you spare me some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We don't have enough right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will rain soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever that girl foretells rain, it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She has never been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. There's a big puddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how fast you run, \Nyou'll never catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's try anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teru! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm digging a well there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The one in the village always dries up during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can take a break once the rain is here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go away again when that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rather travel around all by yourself instead of settling down here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan on living in any one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least come by more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You decided to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious to see how you'll make it rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came here to foretell the rain's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think anyone is capable of {\i1}causing{\i0} the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No normal person could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone able to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,would no longer be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru, rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessed rain!{same phrase as in the first scene}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An epidemic's broken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of this ceaseless rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When will this rain... finally end?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryou—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to howl and cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't even shed a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your aunt has agreed to take care of you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once things improve,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you can live here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What horrible rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that girl's home village devastated by rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, we'll suffer the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though she brought the rain with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The village is back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's as though she brought the rain with her.{ouch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know how this happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I know is that I have no home to return to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and no place I can make my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't even have tears I can shed to accept that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have food from our stockpile, \Nso it's nothing special, but please help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you save the celebrations until after the rain comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't want to wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is today too early to hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss Teru, do you think it'll be much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll come very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally it would be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still no rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What could be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better finish the well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder! Please let us talk to Miss Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days have you been saying {\i1}that{\i0} for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've used up all our water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone spare a little more water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That was the last we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain! When will it rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Te... ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll rain soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring you some water right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look too happy, \Neven though it rained just like you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you still need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed something while watching you over the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in this heat, I haven't seen a single drop of sweat on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you can't shed tears either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you ever caught something you shouldn't have been able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something I shouldn't have been able to catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! That puddle isn't running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the puddle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you. It was a mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mirage...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one form of the Amefurashi, or "Rainmaker" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They normally hang suspended in air like fine water droplets,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but they fall to the ground once they gather enough moisture to cause rain to form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they return to the air as the water evaporates
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and gather rain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the land is stricken by drought and there is no moisture in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they pool near the ground's surface \Nand take on a mirage-like appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from the fact that they are alive, \Nthey are essentially a natural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We call such mushi "drifters."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They wander without a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came in contact with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they took over the moisture within your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they continually rise from you, gathering rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They did all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them out of my body at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no treatment for drifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only wait for their lifespan to reach an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's taking longer for the rain to appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it may mean that they are weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to despair about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This rain of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,has claimed the lives of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I almost killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have to shoulder the burden of those lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were not at fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and neither were the Amefurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just an unfortunate twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you've already figured out a relatively good way to coexist with the Amefurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's not {\i1}all{\i0} bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once the rain stops
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I can shed true tears again,{sup futsuu}{PLS}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will put down roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will continue to drift like the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rain by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange rain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but it's beautiful all the same.
